  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Hundreds of the world's top minds debate ethics at Dstl's AI Fest
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Dstl - the science inside UK defence and security – is playing a critical role in helping the UK MOD understand how it can responsibly and ethically adopt AI.</p>

  </div>
</div>

<div class="govuk-grid-row">
